.IX Header "SEE ALSO"
The \s-1PAR\s0 homepage at <http://par.perl.org>.
.PP
PAR::Tutorial, \s-1PAR::FAQ\s0 (For a more
current \s-1FAQ,\s0 refer to the homepage.)
.PP
