par.pl, parl, pp.
.PP
PAR::Dist for details on \s-1PAR\s0 distributions.
.PP
PAR::Repository::Client for details on accessing \s-1PAR\s0 repositories.
PAR::Repository for details on how to set up such a repository.
.PP
